      <body>
         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1917-04-28">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1917-04-28">28/4</date> Vm. allerlei geordnet und vorbereitet, Briefe, Rechnungen.</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nm. am <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_6436">Fldb.</rs>―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nach dem N. bei <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50461" ref="#person_19784"><surname>Schmutzers</surname></rs>. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50462" ref="#person_19850"><surname>Schönherr</surname></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50463" ref="#person_16419"><surname>Hupka’s</surname></rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50464"><surname>Oppenheimers</surname></rs> (<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50465" ref="#person_18571"><surname>Zierer</surname></rs>). 
Billard. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50466" ref="#person_16419"><surname>Hupka</surname></rs> erzählte <rs type="place" xml:id="pl_10484" ref="#place_cc902382324dee61665fee3034aa4de2" ana="#exclude">oesterreich.</rs> Verwaltungs- und Justizskandale, 
<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_50467"><surname>Opp.</surname></rs> sprach von Kunstauctionen.</p>
         </div>
